      • setGeometry

        public void setGeometry(Geometry geometry)
        Set the geometry. Updates the empty flag and if the geometry is not null, the extended flag. Following invoking this method and upon setting the SRS id, call toBytes() to convert the geometry to bytes. Alternatively call setGeometryToBytes(Geometry) or setGeometryAndBuildEnvelopeToBytes(Geometry) to perform both operations.
        Parameters:
        geometry - geometry
